        <profileDesc>
            <creation/>
            <abstract>
                <p>The work is a prayer in the name of foreign and Ethiopian saints and martyrs. 
                    This work also includes a list of Ethiopian place names associated with Ethiopian saints. 
                    However, as the beginning and ending of the work are missing, the work lacks a clear title.
                    </p>
                 </abstract>
